=== Constructor edge cases ===
Keyword args: Template.__new__ only accepts *args arguments
Invalid type: Template.__new__ *args need to be of type 'str' or 'Interpolation', got int
Invalid interp: interpolations tuple must contain only Interpolation objects, got int
Tuple constructor: hello42world

=== Binary operations ===
Template+str: can only concatenate Template (not "str") to Template
str+Template: unsupported types for __add__: 'str', 'Template'
int+Template: TypeError
-: unsupported
*: unsupported
/: unsupported
%: unsupported
**: unsupported
&: unsupported
|: unsupported
^: unsupported
<<: unsupported
>>: unsupported

=== Edge cases ===
Empty template: ''
Empty strings: [Interpolation(1, 'a', None, ''), Interpolation(2, 'b', None, '')]
Adjacent: '123'
Single iter: ['only']
Self+self: 'testtest'

